{"tid":1948382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（推到全世界睇到）唔想再有手足比狗咬，大家就要學習上暗網","createTime":"2020-03-29T03:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T14:54:27.000Z","uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec7e8aa86927603c962905b30774a25139f6ff9","tid":1948382,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"關於暗網介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.webhostingsecretrevealed.net/zh-TW/blog/web-tools/tourist-guide-to-dark-web-accessing-the-dark-web-tor-browser-and-onion-websites/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webhostingsecretrevealed.net%2Fzh-TW%2Fblog%2Fweb-tools%2Ftourist-guide-to-dark-web-accessing-the-dark-web-tor-browser-and-onion-websites%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=da9d8162\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.webhostingsecretrevealed.net/zh-TW/blog/web-tools/tourist-guide-to-dark-web-accessing-the-dark-web-tor-browser-and-onion-websites/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以自行Google，大把關於暗網的教學可以隨便睇，大家可以自行學習。在連登顯然不適合講太多。大家可以善用暗網，例如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">使用暗網email進行較難截取的通訊</span></strong>，以及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學習各種稀奇古怪的新技能</span></strong>和<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">網購各種新奇的玩意</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要警告：任何人在互聯網上亦必須遵守法律，<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span>在暗網進行違法活動或購買軍火彈藥、危險品、毒品、違禁品等物品。<span style=\"color: red;\">暗網上會有執法人員監測和放蛇，大家切勿以身試法</span> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家留言補充以及開新po討論。<br />\n<br />\n得閒麻煩幫我推埋舊po:<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52034387f73be6bc77b1b5d5ed10581c548be18c","tid":1948382,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞好似有個網絡瀏覽器叫Tor Browser<br />\n聽人講過但自己未用過唔知咩野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f5b9b2db51f328e2d351b8db50a4d3b9f273a5","tid":1948382,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52034387f73be6bc77b1b5d5ed10581c548be18c","tid":1948382,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞好似有個網絡瀏覽器叫Tor Browser<br />\n聽人講過但自己未用過唔知咩野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"tor browser係用來上暗網的瀏覽器，好重要，用一般瀏覽器上唔到暗網"},{"pid":"9c4d29a5d5f6861c976c8b9663de6c4666c6382b","tid":1948382,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52f5b9b2db51f328e2d351b8db50a4d3b9f273a5","tid":1948382,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52034387f73be6bc77b1b5d5ed10581c548be18c","tid":1948382,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞好似有個網絡瀏覽器叫Tor Browser<br />\n聽人講過但自己未用過唔知咩野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"tor browser係用來上暗網的瀏覽器，好重要，用一般瀏覽器上唔到暗網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，長知識了<br />\n睇黎呢個咁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">危險</s